msgid "Pattern Configuration"
msgstr "Desen Ayarları"

msgid ""
"Define the license key format using placeholders:<br>• <code>{RANDOM:N}</"
"code> - N random characters<br>• <code>{CHECKSUM:N}</code> - N-digit "
"checksum<br>• <code>{PREFIX}</code> - Template prefix<br>• <code>{SUFFIX}</"
"code> - Template suffix<br>• <code>{ORDER_ID}</code> - Order number<br>• "
"<code>{PRODUCT_SKU}</code> - Product SKU<br>• <code>{DATE:FORMAT}</code> - "
"Date (YYMMDD, YYYYMMDD, etc.)"
msgstr ""
"Yer tutucular kullanarak lisans anahtar formatını tanımlayın:<br>• "
"<code>{RANDOM:N}</code> - N rastgele karakter<br>• <code>{CHECKSUM:N}</code> "
"- N haneli kontrol toplamı<br>• <code>{PREFIX}</code> - Şablon öneki<br>• "
"<code>{SUFFIX}</code> - Şablon sonu<br>• <code>{ORDER_ID}</code> - Sipariş "
"numarası<br>• <code>{PRODUCT_SKU}</code> - Ürün SKU'su<br>• <code>{DATE:"
"FORMAT}</code> - Tarih (YYMMDD, YYYYMMDD vb.)"

